{"tid":342431,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"信報：李小加去信積金局　倡 MPF 可加碼買A股","createTime":"2017-07-31T15:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T05:20:37.000Z","uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd29595a950692bd93a1a62d7dc9424b726c8b12","tid":342431,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"《信報》今日頭版引述消息指出，港交所行政總裁李小加把握時機去信強積金管理局，促請局方把A股市場納入可供強積金（MPF）投資的「核准港外證券交易所名單」（MPF核准名單）。<br />\n<br />\n港交所發言人回應報道時稱，不評論市場傳聞。根據強積金條例（第485章）第III部的核准交易所指引，目前共有33個國家或地區的交易所獲列入MPF核准名單，當中並未包括A股；條例指出，投資非核准範圍資產的比例，最多不能超過10%，故此目前MPF若要投資A股，規模限於有關比例。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，李小加此舉是希望讓基金界推出佔A股比重較大的MPF產品，為打工仔提供更多選擇；二來有利港交所日後與內地洽商中港互聯互通合作時，有更多談判籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%80-%E5%80%A1-mpf-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E8%B2%B7a%E8%82%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2580%25A1-mpf-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7a%25E8%2582%25A1%2F&d=7xwA1LCTBZptFpxobPm7ri7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9df90a2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2580%25A1-mpf-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7a%25E8%2582%25A1%2F&h=deb8455c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%80-%E5%80%A1-mpf-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E8%B2%B7a%E8%82%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"281af3c9cc351d39c4f4832d491a0ee77de3aa77","tid":342431,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep